heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/huong-dan-quan-ly-chien-dich-zalo-ads-tren-zalo-oa-cua-ban.html\/#1_Cac_chi_so_trong_bao_cao\" title=\"1. C\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 trong b\u00e1o c\u00e1o\">1. C\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 trong b\u00e1o c\u00e1o<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/huong-dan-quan-ly-chien-dich-zalo-ads-tren-zalo-oa-cua-ban.html\/#2_Quan_ly_cac_chi_so_quang_cao\" title=\"2. Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o\">2. Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/huong-dan-quan-ly-chien-dich-zalo-ads-tren-zalo-oa-cua-ban.html\/#Chi_so_CTR\" title=\"Ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 CTR\">Ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 CTR<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/huong-dan-quan-ly-chien-dich-zalo-ads-tren-zalo-oa-cua-ban.html\/#Gia_dau_thau\" title=\"Gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea7u\">Gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea7u<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/huong-dan-quan-ly-chien-dich-zalo-ads-tren-zalo-oa-cua-ban.html\/#So_luong_luot_nhan\" title=\"S\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u01b0\u1ee3t nh\u1ea5n\">S\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u01b0\u1ee3t nh\u1ea5n<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u1ea1n c\u00e1ch theo d\u00f5i c\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1ea1n trong vi\u1ec7c qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00ec khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u00e0 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 mong \u0111\u1ee3i.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15394\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15394\" style=\"width: 2084px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15394 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/zad_website_blog-072.jpg\" alt=\"Quan-ly-chien-dich-zalo-ads\" width=\"2084\" height=\"1251\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/zad_website_blog-072.jpg 2084w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/zad_website_blog-072-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/zad_website_blog-072-1024x615.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/zad_website_blog-072-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/zad_website_blog-072-1536x922.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/zad_website_blog-072-2048x1229.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2084px) 100vw, 2084px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15394\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch zalo ads<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Cac_chi_so_trong_bao_cao\"><\/span>1. C\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 trong b\u00e1o c\u00e1o<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>T\u1ea1i\u00a0<strong>Trang ch\u1ee7<\/strong>, nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o nh\u1ea5n v\u00e0o tab\u00a0<strong>Chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch<\/strong>\u00a0v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn\u00a0<strong>Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15395\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15395\" style=\"width: 700px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15395 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/image-7-700x412-1-700x412-700x412-1.png\" alt=\"quan-ly-chien-dich\" width=\"700\" height=\"412\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/image-7-700x412-1-700x412-700x412-1.png 700w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/image-7-700x412-1-700x412-700x412-1-300x177.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15395\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch<\/dd>\n<dd><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>B\u00e1o c\u00e1o hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb chi ti\u1ebft:<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15396\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15396\" style=\"width: 700px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15396 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/image-34-700x334-700x334-1.png\" alt=\"Bao-cao-hien-thi\" width=\"700\" height=\"334\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/image-34-700x334-700x334-1.png 700w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/image-34-700x334-700x334-1-300x143.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15396\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">B\u00e1o c\u00e1o hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb<\/dd>\n<dd><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li>Chi ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/li>\n<li>S\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t nh\u1ea5n<\/li>\n<li>S\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb<\/li>\n<li>S\u1ed1 CTR (\u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o)<\/li>\n<li>S\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem<\/li>\n<li>T\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<br \/>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Quan_ly_cac_chi_so_quang_cao\"><\/span>2. Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Chi_so_CTR\"><\/span><strong>Ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 CTR<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Trong c\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 b\u00e1o c\u00e1o, CTR gi\u00fap nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 thu h\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng nh\u1ea5n v\u00e0o hay kh\u00f4ng.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15397\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15397\" style=\"width: 700px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15397 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/CTR-700x243-700x243-1.png\" alt=\"Quan-ly-cac-chi-so-quang-cao\" width=\"700\" height=\"243\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/CTR-700x243-700x243-1.png 700w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/CTR-700x243-700x243-1-300x104.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15397\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/dd>\n<dd><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>rong c\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 b\u00e1o c\u00e1o, CTR gi\u00fap nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 thu h\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng nh\u1ea5n v\u00e0o hay kh\u00f4ng.<\/p>\n<p>CTR = s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t nh\u1ea5p chu\u1ed9t\/ s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb x 100<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Gia_dau_thau\"><\/span><strong>Gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea7u<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng Zalo Ads l\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e1 th\u1ea7u (biding) gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ch\u1ea1y trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, gi\u00e1 th\u1ea7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong ba y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng Zalo Ads.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15398\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15398\" style=\"width: 492px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15398 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/image-35.png\" alt=\"Gia-dau-thau\" width=\"492\" height=\"234\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/image-35.png 492w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/image-35-300x143.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 492px) 100vw, 492px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15398\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea7u<\/dd>\n<dd><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 CTR (ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c gi\u1eefa n\u1ed9i dung v\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o v\u1edbi\u00a0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng Zalo), y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 gi\u00e1 th\u1ea7u gi\u00fap cho qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u01a1n khi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1c qu\u1ea3ng\u00a0 c\u00e1o kh\u00e1c c\u00f9ng ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 CTR v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"So_luong_luot_nhan\"><\/span><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u01b0\u1ee3t nh\u1ea5n<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Khi t\u1ea1o qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tr\u00ean Zalo, nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1ebd l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c qu\u1ea3ngc\u00e1o theo to\u00e0n chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch ho\u1eb7c theo ng\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o theo ng\u00e0y\u00a0<\/strong>: l\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1eb7t\u00a0 theo ng\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ch\u1ecdn lo\u1ea1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o n\u00e0y, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng s\u1ebd ph\u00e2n\u00a0 ph\u1ed1i s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1eb7t theo t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1ebd ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i\u00a0 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft th\u1eddi gian quy \u0111\u1ecbnh.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o theo to\u00e0n chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch\u00a0<\/strong>: l\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1eb7t\u00a0 theo ng\u00e0y, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ch\u1ecdn lo\u1ea1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o n\u00e0y, khi\u00a0 t\u00e0i nguy\u00ean qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u1ee7a Zalo Ads tr\u1ed1ng nhi\u1ec1u th\u00ec h\u1ec7\u00a0th\u1ed1ng s\u1ebd ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i nhanh v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft\u00a0 th\u00fac s\u1edbm h\u01a1n th\u1eddi gian quy \u0111\u1ecbnh.<\/p>\n<p>Sau khi theo d\u00f5i c\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda th\u00f4ng tin qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o, trong ph\u1ea7n Th\u00f4ng tin qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o, b\u1ea1n nh\u1eadn ch\u1ecdn n\u00fat\u00a0<strong>Ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda<\/strong>\u00a0nh\u01b0 b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi:<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15399\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15399\" style=\"width: 700px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15399 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/image-36-700x301-700x301-1.png\" alt=\"CHinh-sua\" width=\"700\" height=\"301\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/image-36-700x301-700x301-1.png 700w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/image-36-700x301-700x301-1-300x129.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15399\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda<\/dd>\n<dd><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Hi v\u1ecdng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00e0 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tr\u00ean Zalo Ad